Package: inkr
Title: All of INKAR Data in a Local DuckDB Database
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Long", "Nguyen", , "long.nguyen@uni-bielefeld.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8878-7386"))
Description: inkr populates a local DuckDB database with all the data from
    <https://www.inkar.de/> and creates an interface in R to the database
    via {DBI}.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.1)
Imports: 
    DBI,
    dbplyr,
    dplyr,
    duckdb,
    snakecase,
    stringi
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
